entries.femaleVariant: I have been informed the operation was a success and that you displayed the work of a true professional.
The operation was far from successful. You let me down, V. Such things happen. But do not make it a habit.
If I see a pattern, I will lose trust. And when I lose my trust, I stop calling. Remember that well, V.
Excellent work, V. May it remain so. I am closing the contract and transferring your fee.
